headline: Morgan Stanley Trims Rollins (ROL) Target Price to $70
summary: Rollins Inc. (NYSE:ROL) is one of the 14 Best Consumer Discretionary Stocks to Buy Right Now. Morgan Stanley, on February 14, trimmed its target price on Rollins by 2.9% to $70 (from $72), but kept its Overweight call. This change in target comes a couple of days after Rollins released its Q4 2025 earnings, on […]
